data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY DECEMBER 2nd FROM 1-3pm  **Welcome and discover the enchanting residence at Miahqueah Court, Fort Wayne. Step through the inviting foyer into a world of timeless charm. The open concept kitchen gently guides you to the inviting backyard or cozy living space. The living room, adorned with a classic gas fireplace, exudes warmth and character, creating a perfect gathering space. Elegant French doors throughout add a touch of sophistication, seamlessly connecting spaces. The large master suite features vaulted ceilings and movie projector. The en-suite master bath is incredibly spacious with dual walk in showers. **This home is not just about style—it's also about modern convenience. With a brand-new garage and roof with extended bay, you can relish the peace of mind that comes with updated amenities. Imagine the joy of having a fresh, well-maintained space to call your own. **Located in the coveted 46815 area, this property offers both tranquility and accessibility. Embrace the unique blend of classic and contemporary living at 7201 Miahqueah Court, where every detail has been thoughtfully crafted to create a truly exceptional home.
